text: Svět kde se žebrá is a 1938 Czechoslovak comedy film, directed by Miroslav Cikán. It stars Hugo Haas, Marie Glázrová, and Ladislav Boháč. ==References== ==External links== *Svět kde se žebrá at the Internet Movie Database Category:1938 films Category:Czechoslovak films Category:Czechoslovak comedy films Category:1938 comedy films Category:Films directed by Miroslav Cikán Category:Czech films Category:Czechoslovak black-and-white films
